trans-unit.source: Represents the navigation of a relationship.

trans-unit.source: The result of this expression is the result of navigating the relationship.
trans-unit.target: この式の結果は、リレーションシップのナビゲーションの結果です。

trans-unit.source: Implements the visitor pattern for expressions that do not produce a result value.
trans-unit.target: 結果値を生成しない式のビジター パターンを実装します。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets an <xref href="System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpression"></xref> that specifies the starting point of the navigation and must be a reference to an entity instance.
